00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:56,199
Wow, I really like that shirt.

298
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:58,299
Here. It's a crane accident. Check out the light source.

299
00:37:58,300 --> 00:37:59,799
He likes my shirt.

300
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,899
-Hey, Betty.
