00:44:55,651 --> 00:44:59,102
Cover the back!

405
00:46:06,700 --> 00:46:10,150
Fire!

406
00:46:32,500 --> 00:46:35,199
People of the city of New York, I am here today

407
00:46:35,200 --> 00:46:37,499
because I fell 62 storeys

408
00:46:37,500 --> 00:46:39,299
